Swordman_Thrust.name: Thrust
Swordman_Thrust.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Push the point of your weapon into enemies, performing a strong piercing attack.

Swordman_Bash.name: Bash
Swordman_Bash.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Inflict damage on an enemy with a powerful attack.

Swordman_GungHo.name: Gung Ho
Swordman_GungHo.desc: Become determined by temporarily increasing your attack, while decreasing your defense.

Swordman_PainBarrier.name: Pain Barrier
Swordman_PainBarrier.desc: Temporarily grants a high resistance to being affected by knock back, knock down or staggered.

Swordman_Restrain.name: Restrain
Swordman_Restrain.desc: Lowers your maximum HP, but your attacks have a high chance of stunning enemies.
Swordman_Restrain.desc2:
Chance of Stunning Enemy: #{CaptionRatio}#%
Maximum HP: -#{CaptionRatio2}#
Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds

Swordman_PommelBeat.name: Pommel Beat
Swordman_PommelBeat.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Strike enemies with the hilt of your sword.
Inflicts additional damage on stunned monsters, and partially ignores the defense of small and medium sized enemies.

Swordman_DoubleSlash.name: Double Slash
Swordman_DoubleSlash.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Perform a side slash on enemies.
Enemies afflicted with [Bleeding] take additional damage.

Highlander_WagonWheel.name: Wagon Wheel
Highlander_WagonWheel.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Perform an upward swing with your weapon, launching an enemy.

Highlander_CartarStroke.name: Cartar Stroke
Highlander_CartarStroke.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Gather up power and use your weapon to attack targets by smashing it to the ground.
Highlander_CartarStroke.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
Casting Time: 0.5 second
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#

Highlander_Crown.name: Crown
Highlander_Crown.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Smack your weapon down on an enemy's head. Temporarily decreases the target's INT and SPR.
Highlander_Crown.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
[Shock] Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#

Highlander_CrossGuard.name: Cross Guard
Highlander_CrossGuard.desc: Take a defensive stance, using your weapon to block. Blocked enemies become vulnerable to [Pierce] attacks.

Highlander_Moulinet.name: Moulinet
Highlander_Moulinet.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Inflict damage on enemies by swinging your sword around to create continuous attacks.

Highlander_SkyLiner.name: Skyliner
Highlander_SkyLiner.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Slash the enemy sideways.
Inflicts additional damage on enemies affected by [Bleeding].

Highlander_CrossCut.name: Crosscut
Highlander_CrossCut.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Charge towards an enemy and cut a cross on their body, afflicting [Bleeding].

Highlander_ScullSwing.name: Skull Swing
Highlander_ScullSwing.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Strike and push an enemy sidewards using the side of your sword. The enemy becomes afflicted with [Armor Break].

Highlander_VerticalSlash.name: Vertical Slash
Highlander_VerticalSlash.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Attack with a descending vertical slash. Deals additional damage on medium and large-type enemies according to how much their defense has been decreased by [Skull Swing]. An additional bonus damage will be applied depending on the amount of harmful effect that have been applied to the enemy.

Peltasta_UmboBlow.name: Umbo Blow
Peltasta_UmboBlow.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Use the bump of your shield to attack enemies. Deals additional damage to enemies staggered by a block.

Peltasta_RimBlow.name: Rim Blow
Peltasta_RimBlow.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Use the edge of your shield to attack enemies. Inflicts additional damage on both petrified and frozen enemies.

Peltasta_SwashBuckling.name: Swash Buckling
Peltasta_SwashBuckling.desc: Hit your shield to provoke nearby enemies making them pursue you.
Peltasta_SwashBuckling.reqStance: OneHandSwordShield, OneHandSpearShield, OneHandSwordDagger, OneHandSpearDagger, RapierAndShield, RapierAndDagger

Peltasta_Guardian.name: Guardian
Peltasta_Guardian.desc: Increases your defense while decreasing your attack. Cannot be used with Gung Ho.

Peltasta_ShieldLob.name: Shield Lob
Peltasta_ShieldLob.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Attack an enemy by throwing your shield. Your shield drops on the targeted area, and your physical defense decreases based on the value of the equipment. The shield may be picked up or it'll automatically return to your inventory after a certain time. The decreased physical defense will return back to normal once your shield is back in the inventory.

Peltasta_HighGuard.name: High Guard
Peltasta_HighGuard.desc: Change to active stance using shield in front. Block and increases while attack and critical decrease.

Peltasta_ButterFly.name: Butterfly
Peltasta_ButterFly.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike] - [Slash]
Use your shield and sword to attack enemies with continuous attacks.

Peltasta_UmboThrust.name: Umbo Thrust
Peltasta_UmboThrust.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Heavily strike enemies using the spikes on your shield. Enemies struck by the skill may temporarily lose the effects from their armors.

Peltasta_Langort.name: Langort
Peltasta_Langort.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Block and strike simultaneously by using both a sword and a shield.

Hoplite_Stabbing.name: Stabbing
Hoplite_Stabbing.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Repeatedly stab enemies with your spear.

Hoplite_Pierce.name: Pierce
Hoplite_Pierce.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Attack by piercing enemies with your spear. The larger an enemy is, the more consecutive hits you deal.
Hoplite_Pierce.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
Medium-type Targets: 2 consecutive attacks
Large-type Targets: 3 consecutive attacks

Hoplite_Finestra.name: Finestra
Hoplite_Finestra.desc: Switch into the Window stance to attack. Increases your critical rate and block, while decreasing evasion.

Hoplite_SynchroThrusting.name: Synchro Thrusting
Hoplite_SynchroThrusting.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce] - [Strike]
Use your spear and shield to attack enemies. Deals additional damage when an attack is countered.
Hoplite_SynchroThrusting.desc2:
Spear Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Shield Attack: #{CaptionRatio}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio2}#%
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#

Hoplite_LongStride.name: Long Stride
Hoplite_LongStride.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Inflicts damage to an enemy by jumping to your designated location.

Hoplite_SpearLunge.name: Spear Lunge
Hoplite_SpearLunge.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Stab an enemy in front of you to make it more vulnerable to [Pierce] attacks.

Hoplite_ThrouwingSpear.name: Spear Throw
Hoplite_ThrouwingSpear.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Attack an enemy by throwing your spear. Your spear will stick into the ground where it was thrown, and your physical attack will be decreased based on the equipment's upgrade count until you pick it up. It automatically returns to you after a certain time.

Centurion_Conscript.name: Conscript
Centurion_Conscript.desc: Create a formation that calls on the squads members.

Centurion_PhalanxFormation.name: Phalanx
Centurion_PhalanxFormation.desc: Change to the Phalanx formation. All of the squad members' block will be focused to the 3 in the front row.

Centurion_TercioFormation.name: Tercio
Centurion_TercioFormation.desc: Change to Tersio Formation. Defense is concentrated on the three frontline players and provokes enemy.

Centurion_WingedFormation.name: Winged Formation
Centurion_WingedFormation.desc: Change to the Crane Wing formation. Decreases the defense of enemies within the formation while targeting the leader.

Centurion_WedgeFormation.name: Wedge Formation
Centurion_WedgeFormation.desc2:
Conveys #{CaptionRatio2}#% attack to squad members
#{CaptionRatio}# successive hits when attacking
Consumes 1% SP every 2 seconds

Centurion_SchiltronFormation.name: Schiltron Formation
Centurion_SchiltronFormation.desc: Change to the Schiltron formation. All squad members will stop at once while raising their weapons to prevent from enemies rushing in.

Centurion_Testudo.name: Testudo
Centurion_Testudo.desc: Switches to the Testudo formation. Increases the defense of all members at the cost of slower movement speed.
Centurion_Testudo.desc2:
Attack: -#{CaptionRatio}#%
Increased defense equal to the decreased attack
Additonal Defense: #{CaptionRatio2}#%
Consumes 1% SP per 2 seconds

Centurion_Rotate.name: Change Direction
Centurion_Rotate.desc: Realign direction of formation to leader's view.
Centurion_Rotate.desc2:
Rearrange in line with leader's direction.
Maximum Level: 1

Centurion_SpecialForceFormation.name: Special Formation
Centurion_SpecialForceFormation.desc: Creates a formation which brings squad members together. The skill cooldown time of the squad members that entered into the formation will be reduced in half. Duration will increase by Skill Level, and the number of members in the squad.
Centurion_SpecialForceFormation.desc2:
Cooldown time reduced by 50%
Minimum/Maximum Duration: #{CaptionRatio}# seconds ~ #{CaptionRatio2}# seconds

Barbarian_Embowel.name: Embowel
Barbarian_Embowel.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Release a powerful stab into an enemy, then kick it away with your foot.

Barbarian_StompingKick.name: Stomping Kick
Barbarian_StompingKick.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Trample down on an enemy while in the air or jumping. Increases attack according to the character's jump height and the boot's evasion.

Barbarian_Cleave.name: Cleave
Barbarian_Cleave.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Release a strong attack on enemies by spinning your body. Increases your critical rate when the attack lands and deals additional damage to a stunned enemy.

Barbarian_HelmChopper.name: Helm Chopper
Barbarian_HelmChopper.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Strike the enemy's head, causing it to become afflicted with [Stun].

Barbarian_Warcry.name: Warcry
Barbarian_Warcry.desc: Shout a warcry that causes your enemies to panic and drop their defense, bolstering your attack proportionally.

Barbarian_Frenzy.name: Frenzy
Barbarian_Frenzy.desc: Increases your attack when you keep repeatedly attacking one particular enemy.

Barbarian_Seism.name: Seism
Barbarian_Seism.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Create an earthshake to stop enemies from attacking. The enemy has a chance to become afflicted with [Stun].

Barbarian_GiantSwing.name: Giant Swing
Barbarian_GiantSwing.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Swing an enemy around, using centrifugal force to throw it away.

Barbarian_Pouncing.name: Pouncing
Barbarian_Pouncing.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Charge forward while slashing, attacking any enemies that block your way.

Cataphract_Impaler.name: Impaler
Cataphract_Impaler.desc:
[Strike]
Impales a small or medium-type monster with a spear. It is possible to attack other enemies with a skewered enemy.
Cataphract_Impaler.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#
Able to use while riding

Cataphract_EarthWave.name: Earth Wave
Cataphract_EarthWave.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Gather up power and use your weapon to attack targets by smashing it to the ground.
Cataphract_EarthWave.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#
Able to use while riding

Cataphract_Trot.name: Trot
Cataphract_Trot.desc: Increases your movement speed while riding.

Cataphract_SteedCharge.name: Steed Charge
Cataphract_SteedCharge.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Inflict shock damage by dashing forward to an enemy in front of you.
Cataphract_SteedCharge.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#
Able to use while riding

Cataphract_DoomSpike.name: Doom Spike
Cataphract_DoomSpike.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Gather force and strongly stab enemy with the tip of your spear.
Cataphract_DoomSpike.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#
Able to use while riding

Cataphract_Rush.name: Rush
Cataphract_Rush.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Twirl your spear overhead to attack enemies.
Cataphract_Rush.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
Maximum Duration: 10 seconds
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#
Able to use while riding

Corsair_JollyRoger.name: Jolly Roger
Corsair_JollyRoger.desc: Place a flag that raises the combat abilities of the pirate crew. A combo is activated if multiple enemies is defeated around the Jolly Roger. Attacking enemies around the Jolly Roger allows you to pillage items at a chance based on your Jolly Roger level. (Combo is only activated if the party leader is a Corsair.)

Corsair_Keelhauling.name: Keel Hauling
Corsair_Keelhauling.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Drag and pull enemies captured with Iron Hook. Enenues receives damage each time it is pulled.

Corsair_UnlockChest.name: Unlock Chest
Corsair_UnlockChest.desc: Unlocks low-leveled treasure chests with a key.

Corsair_DustDevil.name: Dust Devil
Corsair_DustDevil.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
As you spin, attack an enemy repeatedly using a weapon in each hand. The enemy will be immobilized temporarily.
Corsair_DustDevil.reqStance: OneHandSwordDagger, OneHandSpearDagger, RapierAndDagger, OneHandSwordPistol, RapierAndPistol, OneHandSpearPistol

Corsair_SubweaponCancel.name: Double Weapon Assault
Corsair_SubweaponCancel.desc: Temporarily connects your basic attacks and dagger attacks.
Corsair_SubweaponCancel.desc2:
Able to use your dagger
without delay after normal attacks
Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds

Corsair_HexenDropper.name: Hexen Dropper
Corsair_HexenDropper.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Use a weapon in each hand to deal successive strikes on an enemy.
Corsair_HexenDropper.reqStance: OneHandSwordDagger, OneHandSpearDagger, RapierAndDagger, OneHandSwordPistol, RapierAndPistol, OneHandSpearPistol

Corsair_PistolShot.name: Pistol Shot
Corsair_PistolShot.desc:
[Missile]
Fires continuous shots with a pistol to damage multiple enemies ahead.

Doppelsoeldner_DeedsOfValor.name: Deeds of Valor
Doppelsoeldner_DeedsOfValor.desc: When taking damage, your attack speed and attack are increased, but your defense is decreased.
Doppelsoeldner_DeedsOfValor.desc2:
Attack per Stack: +#{CaptionRatio}#%
Defense per Stack: -#{CaptionRatio}#%
Maximum Stacks: #{CaptionRatio2}#
Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds

Doppelsoeldner_Mordschlag.name: Mordschlag
Doppelsoeldner_Mordschlag.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Hold your sword backwards and use its handle to smack down an enemy.

Doppelsoeldner_Double_pay_earn.name: Double Pay Earn
Doppelsoeldner_Double_pay_earn.desc: Doubles your EXP and loot dropped when you defeat an enemy within a certain number of attacks. You take 3x damage while the effect is active, and lose more durability when you become incapable of combat.

Doppelsoeldner_Cyclone.name: Cyclone
Doppelsoeldner_Cyclone.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Use centrifugal force to continuously attack enemies.

Doppelsoeldner_Zornhau.name: Zornhau
Doppelsoeldner_Zornhau.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Inflict damage and put the enemy into a state of shock by making a big slash with all your might.

Doppelsoeldner_Zucken.name: Zucken
Doppelsoeldner_Zucken.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Inflict damage on a frontal enemy through a series of lateral slashes. Deals additional damage to enemies afflicted with [Shock].

Doppelsoeldner_Redel.name: Redel
Doppelsoeldner_Redel.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Deals successive attacks to a frontal enemy by swinging your weapon.

Rodelero_ShieldCharge.name: Shield Charge
Rodelero_ShieldCharge.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Use your shield and dash to push enemies away. Enemies nearby will fall down when hit with the shield.

Rodelero_Montano.name: Montano
Rodelero_Montano.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Attack with a powerful slash on the lower half of an enemy with a chance to paralyze.

Rodelero_TargeSmash.name: Targe Smash
Rodelero_TargeSmash.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Use your shield to inflict damage on an enemy with a powerful smash. Has a chance to afflict [Blind] on the enemy.
Rodelero_TargeSmash.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
[Blind] Duration: 3 seconds
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#

Rodelero_ShieldPush.name: Shield Push
Rodelero_ShieldPush.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Use your shield to interrupt enemies.
The target becomes afflicted with [Unbalanced].

Rodelero_ShieldShoving.name: Shield Shoving
Rodelero_ShieldShoving.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Interrupt an enemy's action by using your shield. The enemy is turned around, and cannot take any actions temporarily.

Rodelero_ShieldBash.name: Shield Bash
Rodelero_ShieldBash.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Attack with your shield. Damaged enemies will have their stats temporarily scrambled.

Rodelero_Slithering.name: Slithering
Rodelero_Slithering.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Hold down the key to crouch and move forward. Increases evasion against enemy attacks and triggers an attack immediately after movement has ended.

Rodelero_ShootingStar.name: Shooting Star
Rodelero_ShootingStar.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Use your shield and sword to successively attack enemies.

Rodelero_HighKick.name: High Kick
Rodelero_HighKick.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Perform a high kick to subdue an enemy. Hit enemies will temporarily take additional Strike damage.
Rodelero_HighKick.reqStance: OneHandSpearPistol, OneHandSwordPistol, OneHandSwordArtefact, OneHandSwordShield, OneHandSwordDagger, OneHandSpearArtefact, OneHandSpearShield, OneHandSpearDagger, RapierAndShield, RapierAndDagger, RapierAndArt

Squire_Arrest.name: Arrest
Squire_Arrest.desc: Bind all enemies, including boss monsters, to prevent them from moving.

Squire_Repair.name: Repair
Squire_Repair.desc: Open a shop to repair damaged equipment. It is possible for repaired equipment to exceed its maximum durability.

Squire_WeaponTouchUp.name: Weapon Maintenance
Squire_WeaponTouchUp.desc: Opens a shop to temper weapons and temporarily increase the attack power of a weapon.
Squire_WeaponTouchUp.desc2:
Increases attack equal to [Skill Level+1]x[Number of Weapon Stars]
Attack Count: #{CaptionRatio2}#
Duration: 1 hour

Squire_ArmorTouchUp.name: Armor Maintenance
Squire_ArmorTouchUp.desc: Opens a shop to temper armor and temporarily increase defense. Repairs tops, bottoms and shields.

Squire_Camp.name: Base Camp
Squire_Camp.desc: Set up a base camp for party members. Party members can use the base camp as storage or for teleportation. The duration of buffs used around the camp will increase.
Squire_Camp.desc2:
Duration: #{CaptionRatio}# hours
Duration of the food effects is at least 30 minutes

Squire_FoodTable.name: Refreshment Table
Squire_FoodTable.desc: Set up a refreshment table to prepare dishes that temporarily increases the abilities of your party members. A refreshment table can only placed near a base camp. If the camp is removed, the refreshment table will be removed as well.
Squire_FoodTable.desc2: Increases the food effectivenes by skill level

Squire_MitigatePenalty.name: Penalty Reduction
Squire_MitigatePenalty.desc: Reduces the penalty from incapable of combat.
Squire_MitigatePenalty.desc2:
Equipment Durability Penalty: -#{CaptionRatio}#%
Consumed Silver Penalty: -#{CaptionRatio2}#%
Consumed Gem Penalty: -#{CaptionTime}#%

Shinobi_Kunai.name: Kunai
Shinobi_Kunai.desc: Attack multiple enemies by throwing a kunai.

Shinobi_Bunshin_no_jutsu.name: Bunshin no Jutsu
Shinobi_Bunshin_no_jutsu.desc: Creates clones of yourself. The clones will act along as a main body and skills can be used along with your clones. The HP of your clones is determined by your DEX.

Shinobi_Mokuton_no_jutsu.name: Mokuton no Jutsu
Shinobi_Mokuton_no_jutsu.desc: Counter-attack by tricking the enemy with a fake doll created from a log.

Shinobi_Katon_no_jutsu.name: Katon no Jutsu
Shinobi_Katon_no_jutsu.desc: Attack multiple enemies by continuously exploding the gunpowder you possess.

Shinobi_Mijin_no_jutsu.name: Mijin no Jutsu
Shinobi_Mijin_no_jutsu.desc: Attack enemies in the area nearby by exploding the gunpowder you have. Using this technique will also damage you and might cause incapability of combat if your HP is too low.

Fencer_Lunge.name: Lunge
Fencer_Lunge.desc: [Physical] - [Pierce]Lower your stance and reach out to attack an enemy. Your evasion rate increases and the enemy becomes more vulnerable to [Slash] attacks.

Fencer_SeptEtoiles.name: Sept Etoiles
Fencer_SeptEtoiles.desc: [Physical] - [Pierce]Stab an enemy with successive strikes.

Fencer_AttaqueCoquille.name: Attaque Coquille
Fencer_AttaqueCoquille.desc: [Physical] - [Strike]Attack an enemy with the guard of your sword. The enemy's defense is ignored when attacked again with [Pierce] attacks.

Fencer_EsquiveToucher.name: Esquive Toucher
Fencer_EsquiveToucher.desc: [Physical] - [Pierce]Move swiftly to avoid enemy attacks and deliver complex successive attacks.

Fencer_Flanconnade.name: Flanconnade
Fencer_Flanconnade.desc: [Physical] - [Slash]Perform a complex upward attack with your rapier. This attack protects you against an enemy attack.

Fencer_AttaqueComposee.name: Attaque Composee
Fencer_AttaqueComposee.desc: [Physical] - [Pierce]Stab an enemy in front of you.

Fencer_Preparation.name: Preparation
Fencer_Preparation.desc: Twirl the tip of your sword to parry an enemy attack and prepare for the next attack. The next [Pierce] attack you make will inflict twice as much damage.
Fencer_Preparation.desc2:
최대 유지시간 #{CaptionRatio2}#초
스킬 유지할 동안 블록 확률 #{CaptionRatio}#% 증가
지속시간 15초

Dragoon_Dragontooth.name: Dragontooth
Dragoon_Dragontooth.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Rotate your spear using centrifugal force to attack an enemy.

Dragoon_Serpentine.name: Serpentine
Dragoon_Serpentine.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Use your spear to deal continuous damage to enemies in front of you.

Dragoon_Gae_Bulg.name: Gae Bulg
Dragoon_Gae_Bulg.desc:
[Physical] - [Stab]
Attack several enemies within a radius by throwing a spear. Damaged enemies will temporarily become weaker to physical property attacks. The thrown spear must be picked up to use it again.

Dragoon_Dragon_Soar.name: Dragon Soar
Dragoon_Dragon_Soar.desc:
[Physical] - [Slash]
Vault into the air while swinging your spear upwards. Enemies hit with this skill are temporarily launched into the air.

Templer_SummonGuildMember.name: Summon Guild Member
Templer_SummonGuildMember.desc: Summons a specific guild member to your location. You need permission from the specific guild member.

Templer_WarpToGuildMember.name: Warp To Guild Member
Templer_WarpToGuildMember.desc: Warps to a specific guild member's location. You cannot warp to guild members who are in an instanced dungeon.
Templer_WarpToGuildMember.desc2: Warp To Specific Guild Member's Location

Templer_BuildGuildTower.name: Build Guild Tower
Templer_BuildGuildTower.desc:
길드 타워의 추가 기능을 사용할 수 있게 해줍니다. 길드 타워는 '길드 타워' 아이템을 사용해서 설치할 수 있습니다.
1레벨: 워프 이용 가능
2레벨: 창고 사용 가능
3레벨: 길드 성장 가능
4레벨: 길드이벤트 이용 가능
5레벨: 길드아지트 가능

Templer_ReduceCraftTime.name: Reduce Craft Time
Templer_ReduceCraftTime.desc: Plant a flag that reduces the crafting time of all guild members in the area nearby. This can only be used nearby a Guild Tower.

Templer_BattleOrders.name: Battle Orders
Templer_BattleOrders.desc: Temporarily increases STR of guild members nearby the guild master. This effect disappears if the guild master is too far away.

Wizard_EnergyBolt.name: Energy Bolt
Wizard_EnergyBolt.desc:
[Magic]
Gather powerful magical energy to launch it towards an enemy. Increases the inflicted damage depending on the amount of gathered energy.
Wizard_EnergyBolt.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
Casting Time: 1 second
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#

Wizard_Lethargy.name: Lethargy
Wizard_Lethargy.desc2:
Physical Attack: -#{CaptionRatio}#
Magic Attack: -#{CaptionRatio}#
Evasion: -#{CaptionRatio2}#
[Lethargy] Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds

Wizard_Sleep.name: Sleep
Wizard_Sleep.desc: Makes an enemy fall asleep. The enemy awakens once you've reached your limit of attacks.

Wizard_ReflectShield.name: Reflect Shield
Wizard_ReflectShield.desc: Creates a protective shield that reflects the amplified damage back to an enemy.

Wizard_EarthQuake.name: Earthquake
Wizard_EarthQuake.desc:
[Magic] - [Earth]
Inflicts damage on an enemy by creating a powerful earthquake in front of you.

Wizard_Surespell.name: Surespell
Wizard_Surespell.desc: Skills being cast cannot be interrupted by enemy attacks.

Wizard_MagicMissile.name: Magic Missile

Druid_Chortasmata.desc: Grass temporarily grows on the targeted area. Monsters within the targeted area become Plant-type monsters.

Druid_ShapeShifting.name: Shape Shifting
Druid_ShapeShifting.desc: Transform into a monster of the Animal-type, Plant-type or Insect-type in front of you for a given duration.
Druid_ShapeShifting.desc2:
Able to use the monster's skill
Maximum Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds

Druid_Telepath.name: Telepath
Druid_Telepath.desc: Penetrate into the mind of an enemy in front of you to control it.

Druid_StereaTrofh.name: Sterea Trofh
Druid_StereaTrofh.desc: Grown grass protects you and your allies. It casts in the place of [Chortasmata] first if exists, otherwise it casts on you.

Druid_Transform.name: Transform
Druid_Transform.desc: Transform back into the monster that you last shape shifted to.
Druid_Transform.desc2:
Able to use the monster's skill
Maximum Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds

Sadhu_OutofBody.name: Out of Body
Sadhu_OutofBody.desc: Move your spirit out of the body. The spirit can only move near the body.

Sadhu_Prakriti.name: Prakriti
Sadhu_Prakriti.desc: Move body to the spirit to unite again. Can only be used when spirit is out of body.

Sadhu_AstralBodyExplosion.name: Astral Body Explosion
Sadhu_AstralBodyExplosion.desc:
[Magic]
Inflict damage on nearby enemies by separating your soul from your body to cause an explosion.

Sadhu_VashitaSiddhi.name: Vashita Siddhi
Sadhu_VashitaSiddhi.desc: Decreases the STR, CON, INT, SPR and DEX of enemies nearby.
Sadhu_VashitaSiddhi.desc2:
STR, CON, INT, SPR, DEX: -#{CaptionRatio}#
Consumes SP per second
Maximum Duration: 10 seconds

Sadhu_Possession.name: Possession
Sadhu_Possession.desc:
[Magic] - [Holy]
Bind enemy to stop its movement and inflict damage.
Sadhu_Possession.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
Up to 5 users
Maximum Duration: 10 seconds

Sadhu_TransmitPrana.name: Transmit Prana
Sadhu_TransmitPrana.desc: Transfer your abilities to allies in front of you.

Dievdirbys_CarveVakarine.name: Carve Vakarine
Dievdirbys_CarveVakarine.desc:
Carve a statue of Vakarine, the goddess of the Evening Star.
You may warp to other areas through the Goddess Statue.
Dievdirbys_CarveVakarine.desc2:
Number of Warps: #{CaptionRatio}#
Goddess Statue Duration: 30 seconds
Consumes 1 Oak Wood

Dievdirbys_CarveZemina.name: Statue of Goddess Zemyna
Dievdirbys_CarveZemina.desc: Carve a statue of Zemyna, the goddess of the earth. Decreases the SP cost and SP recovery time when using skills for nearby allies who are within the radius of the Goddess Statue.
Dievdirbys_CarveZemina.desc2:
Decreases #{CaptionRatio}# SP
SP recovery time decreases by 5 seconds
Statue Duration: #{CaptionRatio2}# seconds
Consumes 1 Pine Wood

Dievdirbys_CarveLaima.name: Statue of Goddess Laima
Dievdirbys_CarveLaima.desc:
Carves a statue of Laima, the goddess of fate.
Decreases the cooldown of your party members' skills within the radius of the Goddess Statue.
Dievdirbys_CarveLaima.desc2:
Cooldown: -#{CaptionRatio}#%
Movement Speed: -20
Statue Duration: #{CaptionRatio2}# seconds
Consumes 1 Cedar Wood

Dievdirbys_Carve.name: Carve Attack
Dievdirbys_Carve.desc:
[Physical] - [Pierce]
Attack the target by using a carving knife. Plant-type monsters take additional bonus damage and may drop statue materials.
Dievdirbys_Carve.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio2}#%
Additional Damage to Plant-type Monsters: +#{CaptionRatio}#
Statue Materials Drop Rate: #{CaptionTime}#%

Dievdirbys_CarveOwl.name: Carve Owl
Dievdirbys_CarveOwl.desc:
[Magic]
Carve an Owl Sculpture to protect yourself from the attacks of enemies in front of you.
Dievdirbys_CarveOwl.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio2}#%
Number of Blocks: #{CaptionRatio}#
Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds
Consumes 2 Oak Wood

Dievdirbys_CarveAustrasKoks.name: Carve World Tree
Dievdirbys_CarveAustrasKoks.desc: Carve a divine World Tree that silences nearby enemies.
Dievdirbys_CarveAustrasKoks.desc2:
Carve Statue Duration: #{CaptionRatio}# seconds
Consumes 1 Ash Wood

Dievdirbys_CarveAusirine.name: Statue of Goddess Ausrine
Dievdirbys_CarveAusirine.desc: Carve a statue of Ausrine, the goddess of the Morning Star. Those in your party who circle around the Goddess Statue counter-clockwise are granted divine protection and become immune to damage temporarily.
Dievdirbys_CarveAusirine.desc2:
[Goddess' Blessing] Duration: #{CaptionRatio}# seconds
Goddess Statue Duration: 30 seconds
Consumes 1 Cedar Wood

Oracle_ArcaneEnergy.name: Arcane Energy
Oracle_ArcaneEnergy.desc: Increases the maximum SP and STA of you and your party members.

Oracle_Change.name: Change
Oracle_Change.desc: Changes the monster in front of you to a different monster with a similar level.

Oracle_Clairvoyance.name: Clairvoyance
Oracle_Clairvoyance.desc: Predict and show which item the monster will drop in advance.

Oracle_CounterSpell.name: Counter Spell
Oracle_CounterSpell.desc2:
Removes nearby Magic Circles
Maximum Duration: 30 seconds
Targets: #{CaptionRatio}#

Oracle_Forecast.name: Forecast
Oracle_Forecast.desc: Show in advance where the enemy will attack you and your party members.

Oracle_Ressetting.name: Resetting
Oracle_Ressetting.desc: Change the item dropped from an enemy to a different item. You will be notified when an item is changed.

Oracle_Prophecy.name: Prophecy
Oracle_Prophecy.desc: Grants a temporary effect preventing Lv. 1 status ailments to nearby party members.

Oracle_DeathVerdict.name: Death Sentence
Oracle_DeathVerdict.desc: Sentence the enemy to death. The sentenced target dies when time is up.

Monk_IronSkin.name: Iron Skin
Monk_IronSkin.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Temper your skin as hard as steel to inflict damage by bouncing back an enemy's attack.
Monk_IronSkin.desc2:
Reflects #{CaptionRatio}#% of the target's physical attack
Maximum Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds
Unable to block magic & long-ranged projectiles

Monk_DoublePunch.name: Double Punch
Monk_DoublePunch.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Use your trained fists to attack an enemy in quick succession.

Monk_PalmStrike.name: Palm Strike
Monk_PalmStrike.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Use your trained fingertips to attack an enemy by inflicting an internal injury.

Monk_HandKnife.name: Hand Knife
Monk_HandKnife.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Strike with a powerful hand knife to deal damage on an enemy.

Monk_EnergyBlast.name: Energy Blast
Monk_EnergyBlast.desc:
[Physical] - [Holy]
Harness energy and release it in front of you, dealing damage and pushing back all enemies in its path.
Monk_EnergyBlast.desc2:
Attack per Hit: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio2}#%
Consumes 30 SP per second

Monk_1InchPunch.name: One Inch Punch
Monk_1InchPunch.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Extend your fist from a close distance to destroy the insides of an enemy. The attacked enemy will steadily lose HP and SP.

Monk_God_Finger_Flicking.name: God Finger Flick
Monk_God_Finger_Flicking.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Throw a coin by using the tip of your finger to inflict damage on an enemy.

Monk_Golden_Bell_Shield.name: Golden Bell Shield
Monk_Golden_Bell_Shield.desc: Change to a state where you become temporarily invincible from all attacks.
Monk_Golden_Bell_Shield.desc2:
Maximum Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds
Able to block magic & long-ranged projectiles

Pardoner_Simony.name: Simony
Pardoner_Simony.desc: Craft your skill into a scroll that anyone can use.

Pardoner_Indulgentia.name: Indulgentia
Pardoner_Indulgentia.desc: Use a ritual to cure allies with a Lv2 status ailment or to inflict damage on enemies.
Pardoner_Indulgentia.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio2}#%
Attacks #{CaptionRatio}# enemies
Cures the entire party
Cures #{CaptionRatio}# allies
Consumes 500 silver

Pardoner_DiscernEvil.name: Discerning Evil
Pardoner_DiscernEvil.desc: Extend the duration of harmful effects applied to an enemy.

Pardoner_IncreaseMagicDEF.name: Increase Magic Defense
Pardoner_IncreaseMagicDEF.desc: Temporarily increases the magic defense of you and your party members.

Pardoner_Oblation.name: Oblation
Pardoner_Oblation.desc: Open an offering box to receive donations in the form of items from allies. Can only be opened nearby a Goddess Statue. Cannot be opened in town.

Pardoner_SpellShop.name: Spell Shop
Pardoner_SpellShop.desc: Open a shop to sell your skills with beneficial effects.
Pardoner_SpellShop.desc2:
Able to register skills that consume items
Additional Duration: #{CaptionRatio}# minutes

Pardoner_Dekatos.name: Decatose
Pardoner_Dekatos.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Attack an enemy by collecting money to offer to the gods. Enemies, with the exception of boss monsters, can be instantly killed at a 10% chance and the offered money can be picked back up again.

Paladin_Smite.name: Smite
Paladin_Smite.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Strike down enemies with a powerful attack. Deals double damage to Mutant and Devil-type enemies.

Paladin_Restoration.name: Restoration
Paladin_Restoration.desc: Activate aura and increase HP recovery of allies nearby.

Paladin_ResistElements.name: Resist Elements
Paladin_ResistElements.desc: Temporarily increases the Fire, Ice, Lightning, Poison and Earth property resistances of you and your party members and has a chance of nullifying the listed property attacks. Decreases the magic defense of nearby enemies on cast.
Paladin_ResistElements.desc2:
Property Resistance: +#{CaptionRatio}#
Nullification Chance: #{CaptionRatio2}#%
Enemy's Magic Defense: -#{SkillFactor}#
Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds

Paladin_TurnUndead.name: Turn Undead
Paladin_TurnUndead.desc: Has a chance of instantly defeating Mutant or Devil-type enemies.

Paladin_Conversion.name: Conversion
Paladin_Conversion.desc: Creates a magic circle which has a chance of converting enemies.

Paladin_Barrier.name: Barrier
Paladin_Barrier.desc: Push enemies away and create a barrier of protection which doesn't allow others to enter for some time. Increases the magic defense of allies who are inside the barrier.

Paladin_Conviction.name: Conviction
Paladin_Conviction.desc:
[Physical] - [Strike]
Attacks an enemy as an attack for the betrayer. Resistance to Fire, Ice, Lightning, Poison of the enemy that received the attack will decrease.
Paladin_Conviction.desc2:
Attack: #{SkillAtkAdd}#
Attribute Damage: #{CaptionRatio}#%
AoE Attack Ratio: #{SkillSR}#
All Properties Resistance: -#{CaptionRatio2}#

PlagueDoctor_HealingFactor.name: Healing Factor
PlagueDoctor_HealingFactor.desc:
[Magic] - [Holy]
Temporarily creates a magic circle that grants a healing factor. HP will be quickly recovered if you or your allies take damage from an enemy inside the magic circle.

PlagueDoctor_Incineration.name: Incineration
PlagueDoctor_Incineration.desc:
[Magic] - [Fire]
Incinerate enemies with status ailments. The duration of [Incineration] will increase depending on the amount of status ailments on enemies.

PlagueDoctor_Bloodletting.name: Bloodletting
PlagueDoctor_Bloodletting.desc: Temporarily let you or your allies bleed to prevent further status ailments. This state will be invulnerable to all rank 2 or lower status ailments.

PlagueDoctor_Fumigate.name: Fumigate
PlagueDoctor_Fumigate.desc: Spray a cloud of antidote that cures the status ailments of an ally. Allies within the effect will be cured of rank 3 or lower status ailments.
PlagueDoctor_Fumigate.desc2:
Removes rank 3 and lower status ailments
Applies a maximum of #{CaptionRatio}# times

PlagueDoctor_Pandemic.name: Pandemic
PlagueDoctor_Pandemic.desc: Spread all status ailments on targeted enemies to other enemies within the range.

PlagueDoctor_BeakMask.name: Beak Mask
PlagueDoctor_BeakMask.desc: Equip the Bird Beak Mask. The front side of the mask has a special drug that prevents rank 2 or lower status ailments from affecting you.
PlagueDoctor_BeakMask.desc2:
Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds
100% Immunity to Rank 1 and 2
80% Immunity to Rank 3

Kabbalist_RevengedSevenfold.name: Revenged Sevenfold
Kabbalist_RevengedSevenfold.desc:
[Magic] - [Holy]
Use the power of the goddess to avenge yourself with x7 the power of an enemy's attack.

Kabbalist_Ayin_sof.name: Ein Sof
Kabbalist_Ayin_sof.desc:
[Magic] - [Holy]
Creates a magic circle that drastically increases your maximum HP for a period of time.
Kabbalist_Ayin_sof.desc2:
Duration: #{CaptionTime}# seconds
Magic Circle Duration: #{CaptionRatio2}# seconds
Maximum HP: +#{CaptionRatio}#%

Kabbalist_Merkabah.name: Merkabah
Kabbalist_Merkabah.desc:
[Magic] - [Holy]
Summons the wagon of the goddess to attack enemies.

Kabbalist_Gematria.name: Gematria
Kabbalist_Gematria.desc: Divide the numbers of an enemy's name and calculate a new number.

Kabbalist_Notarikon.name: Notarikon
Kabbalist_Notarikon.desc: Calculate a new number from the first and the last letter of an enemy's name.

Kabbalist_Reduce_Level.name: Reduce Level
Kabbalist_Reduce_Level.desc: Decrease the level of an enemy depending on the calculated number.

Chaplain_LastRites.name: Last Rites
Chaplain_LastRites.desc: Makes the attacks of party members have the Holy property. Increases Holy property damage in proportion to the caster's [Sacrament] level which becomes more powerful when HP is below 40%.

Chaplain_BuildCappella.name: Deploy Capella
Chaplain_BuildCappella.desc: Deploys a temporary sacellum with a wrapped cloak. The caster and party members are able to simultaneously receive the effects of the caster's Aspersion, Monstrance, Blessing, Sacrament, Stone Skin.
Chaplain_BuildCappella.desc2:
Cappella Duration: #{CaptionRatio}# seconds
Effect Duration: #{CaptionRatio2}# seconds
Consumes 1 Cape

Chaplain_MagnusExorcismus.name: Magnus Exorcismus
Chaplain_MagnusExorcismus.desc: Transforms the Exorcise Magic Circle in front of the caster into an enormous pillar of exorcism. This divine pillar of light continues to damage nearby enemies.

Chaplain_Aspergillum.name: Aspergillum
Chaplain_Aspergillum.desc: Fills the equipped weapon with holy water and makes it splash with every attack. The level of holy water being used is the same level as the caster's [Aspersion].
